# Example Tor client configuration (documentation only)

ClientOnly 1
ExitRelay 0
ORPort 0
DirPort 0

ClientUseIPv4 1
ClientUseIPv6 0

AvoidDiskWrites 1

# Conservative circuit rotation example (adjust as needed)
MaxCircuitDirtiness 600
NewCircuitPeriod 30

# Tor SOCKS typically stays local on Debian-based systems.
# Exposing SOCKS to VPN clients should be done via a controlled forwarder.
SocksPort 127.0.0.1:9050
